    "form_header_text": "FY27 Appropriations Requests Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "Thank you for expressing interest in submitting an appropriations request to our office. Know that we will only prioritize requests that have a direct presence or impact on Washington's 9th District. For your awareness, because of Rep. Smith's role as Ranking Member of the defense authorizing committee (HASC), he has traditionally been restrained in making requests of the Defense Appropriations Subcommittee (HAC-D/DOD Approps). The deadline for submission is Friday, March 6th.",
