            "label": "Will you be submitting this request to the House Armed Services Committee as a legislative proposal for the FY2027 National Defense Authorization Act (NDAA)?",
            "help_text": "Note that the NDAA deadline is Friday, February 13th by 6pm ET. Legislative proposals will not be accepted after this deadline. Note in the comments if POC/Org info differs between requests.",
